{"id": "302407", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=302407", "title": "Zuni", "text": "Zuni is a &lt;a href=\"Darkspear%20tribe\"&gt;Darkspear&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"jungle%20troll\"&gt;troll&lt;/a&gt; recruit who accompanies new &lt;a href=\"Troll%20%28playable%29\"&gt;troll&lt;/a&gt; players on several quests throughout levels 1-5. He is first seen next to the player after first logging on. Accepting the quest to find the first class trainer will have him greet you and run towards the training grounds. You later meet him again when you have completed your training and are tasked with the quest &lt;a href=\"A%20Troll%27s%20Truest%20Companion\"&gt;A Troll's Truest Companion&lt;/a&gt; and talks to you as you cross the bridge to help obtain raptors. During two later quests &lt;a href=\"No%20More%20Mercy\"&gt;No More Mercy&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Territorial%20Fetish\"&gt;Territorial Fetish&lt;/a&gt; he assists you in killing the &lt;a href=\"naga\"&gt;naga&lt;/a&gt; that are trying to take over the Echo Isles, led by &lt;a href=\"Zar%27jira\"&gt;Zar'jira&lt;/a&gt;. Near the end of the fight with Zar'jira during the quest &lt;a href=\"An%20Ancient%20Enemy\"&gt;An Ancient Enemy&lt;/a&gt; he runs behind her to stamp out the braziers that fuel her powers. Zar'jira notices what he is doing and casts a Frostwave, killing him instantly. After being killed, &lt;a href=\"Vol%27jin\"&gt;Vol'jin&lt;/a&gt; asks &lt;a href=\"Vanira\"&gt;Vanira&lt;/a&gt; to heal Zuni, but when she attempts to do so she finds out that Zar'jira ripped his soul from his body, forever killing him. "}
