{"id": "25032", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=25032", "title": "Recipe of the Kaldorei", "text": "Recipe of the Kaldorei is an &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; only &lt;a href=\"cooking\"&gt;cooking&lt;/a&gt; quest in &lt;a href=\"Teldrassil\"&gt;Teldrassil&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"night%20elf\"&gt;night elf&lt;/a&gt; starting zone. In this quest, players are sent by &lt;a href=\"Zarrin\"&gt;Zarrin&lt;/a&gt; the cook to gather spider legs for a special dish unique to the &lt;a href=\"kaldorei\"&gt;kaldorei&lt;/a&gt;.\nObjectives.\nCollect 7 &lt;a href=\"Small%20Spider%20Leg\"&gt;Small Spider Leg&lt;/a&gt;s for &lt;a href=\"Zarrin\"&gt;Zarrin&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Dolanaar\"&gt;Dolanaar&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nLong ago, the night elves were called the &lt;a href=\"kaldorei\"&gt;kaldorei&lt;/a&gt;, a name that means \"children of the stars.\" Learning of the past is an important step in your path as a &lt;class&gt;, &lt;name&gt;, so listen well to what I have to tell you.\nThe kaldorei have always taken much pride in their harmonious relationship with nature. This means that we only take from nature what is necessary, and that we return in kind. This balance has afforded us much, &lt;name&gt;.\nGo out and collect seven small spider legs -- no more than that, and return to me.\nReward.\nYou will receive \nProgress.\nRemember the balance, &lt;name&gt;. I wish you to develop an understanding and a strong empathy for the living forests.\nCompletion.\nAlways remember what I have shown you today, &lt;name&gt;. You are part of the balance that the night elves strive to keep intact, even during troublesome times.\nWalkthrough.\nObtaining this quest.\nYou must have the secondary profession &lt;a href=\"cooking\"&gt;cooking&lt;/a&gt; to obtain this quest. You can train it from the same NPC who gives the quest, &lt;a href=\"Zarrin\"&gt;Zarrin&lt;/a&gt;. He can be found standing near a cauldron behind the &lt;a href=\"Dolanaar\"&gt;Dolanaar&lt;/a&gt; inn (south of the road).\nCompleting this quest.\nThe spider legs needed to complete the quest (and used in the recipe which you receive as a reward) drop from all the spiders in &lt;a href=\"Teldrassil\"&gt;Teldrassil&lt;/a&gt;, except those in &lt;a href=\"Shadowglen\"&gt;Shadowglen&lt;/a&gt;. It's best to complete this quest as you travel around for other quests in the area, killing spiders as you go. When you have gathered enough legs, return to &lt;a href=\"Zarrin\"&gt;Zarrin&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Dolanaar\"&gt;Dolanaar&lt;/a&gt; to complete the quest. Note that while you can receive the reward with any cooking skill, you must have cooking 10 in order to learn the recipe."}
