{"id": "659596", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=659596", "title": "Reconstructing \"Fear and Flesh\" (2)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"Fear and Flesh\" from Corrupted or Lost Areas within &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Visions\"&gt;Horrific Visions&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nAdherents of the &lt;a href=\"Old%20God\"&gt;Old God&lt;/a&gt;s maintain that flesh is a gift, not &lt;a href=\"Curse%20of%20Flesh\"&gt;a curse&lt;/a&gt;. This tome reflects on the Old Gods' supposed benevolence in granting us such a generous blessing.\nNaturally, it omits any mention of what occurs when their corruption is allowed to run unfettered.\nGather more of these pages for me. As wretched as these words might be, studying them will allow us to increase the efficacy of your cloak.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nAnything to share?\nCompletion.\nI see you have found more pages from the book. Well done.\nNotes.\nThis quest was first offered in the third week of &lt;a href=\"patch%208.3\"&gt;patch 8.3&lt;/a&gt;. As in the previous quest, the completion of two of the mid-level sections of the vision is required, not necessarily the defeat of the final boss."}
{"id": "659949", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=659949", "title": "Reconstructing \"Fear and Flesh\" (3)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"Fear and Flesh\" from Corrupted or Lost Areas within &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Visions\"&gt;Horrific Visions&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nAdherents of the &lt;a href=\"Old%20God\"&gt;Old God&lt;/a&gt;s maintain that flesh is a gift, not &lt;a href=\"Curse%20of%20Flesh\"&gt;a curse&lt;/a&gt;. This tome reflects on the Old Gods' supposed benevolence in granting us such a generous blessing.\nNaturally, it omits any mention of what occurs when their corruption is allowed to run unfettered.\nGather more of these pages for me. As wretched as these words might be, studying them will allow us to increase the efficacy of your cloak.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nNearly halfway there, &lt;name&gt;.\nHave you found anything new?\nCompletion.\nMagnificent. Our work is coming together nicely.\nNotes.\nFirst offered in the fourth week of &lt;a href=\"Patch%208.3.0\"&gt;patch 8.3&lt;/a&gt;, Wrathion now requires at minimum 2 runs of a &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Vision\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt; to acquire the necessary items. As before, completing only the mid-level difficulty areas is the objective here. The defeat of the final boss (Alleria or Thrall) is not required."}
{"id": "660327", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=660327", "title": "Reconstructing \"Fear and Flesh\" (4)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"Fear and Flesh\" from Corrupted or Lost Areas within &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Visions\"&gt;Horrific Visions&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nPerhaps the most insidious element of the &lt;a href=\"Old%20God\"&gt;Old God&lt;/a&gt;s' whispers is that they contain within them the smallest kernel of truth. There is something to be said for the joy that comes with feeling the sun on one's skin and the wind in one's hair.\nBut you have braved &lt;a href=\"N%27Zoth\"&gt;N'Zoth's&lt;/a&gt; visions. You have seen where their designs are ultimately meant to lead. The curse of flesh has nothing to do with bringing us joy.\nContinue to collect the pages of this book. We have nearly finished piecing it back together.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nMaking progress?\nCompletion.\nThe words in this tome build and expand on the writings from the one we completed previously.\nStay the course, &lt;name&gt;. I expect we shall have answers soon enough.\nNotes.\nFirst offered in the fifth week of &lt;a href=\"Patch%208.3.0\"&gt;patch 8.3&lt;/a&gt;, Wrathion now requires an absolute minimum of 2, though likely 3 or more, runs of a &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Vision\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt; to acquire the necessary items. As before, completing only the mid or high-level difficulty areas is the objective here. The defeat of the final boss (Alleria or Thrall) is not required.\nBefore \"Shadowlands\", 6 quest items were the objective."}
{"id": "660849", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=660849", "title": "Reconstructing \"Fear and Flesh\" (5)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"Fear and Flesh\" from Corrupted or Lost Areas within &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Visions\"&gt;Horrific Visions&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nPerhaps the most insidious element of the Old Gods' whispers is that they contain within them the smallest kernel of truth. There is something to be said for the joy that comes with feeling the sun on one's skin and the wind in one's hair.\nBut you have braved &lt;a href=\"N%27Zoth\"&gt;N'Zoth&lt;/a&gt;'s visions. You have seen where their designs are ultimately meant to lead. The &lt;a href=\"curse%20of%20flesh\"&gt;curse of flesh&lt;/a&gt; has nothing to do with bringing us joy.\nContinue to collect the pages of this book. We have nearly finished piecing it back together.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nThe darkness lingers.\nNever hurried. Never sleeping. Patiently waiting...\nCompletion.\nAh, the final pages.\nI believe we're ready to advance our efforts yet again, dear &lt;name&gt;.\nNotes.\nFirst offered in the sixth week of &lt;a href=\"Patch%208.3.0\"&gt;patch 8.3&lt;/a&gt;, Wrathion now requires an absolute minimum of three, though likely four or more, runs of a &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Vision\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt; to acquire the necessary items. As before, completing only the mid or high-level difficulty areas is the objective here. The defeat of the final boss (Alleria or Thrall) is not required.\nBefore \"Shadowlands\", 8 quest items were the objective."}
{"id": "658524", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=658524", "title": "Reconstructing \"The Curse of Stone\"", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"The Curse of Stone\" from &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Vision\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt;s for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nI came across several references to this book in my research of &lt;a href=\"Ny%27alotha\"&gt;Ny'alotha&lt;/a&gt;. Penned by a neophyte cultist, it documents the \"lies of the &lt;a href=\"Titans\"&gt;Titans&lt;/a&gt;\" and the \"injustices\" they inflicted upon the denizens of &lt;a href=\"Azeroth\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt;.\nMad ravings, intended to erode the reader's acceptance of reality.\nStill, by studying this work, we can gain a better understanding of the &lt;a href=\"Old%20God\"&gt;Old God&lt;/a&gt;'s power, and thus tailor &lt;a href=\"Ashjra%27kamas%2C%20Shroud%20of%20Resolve\"&gt;the cloak&lt;/a&gt; to offer better protection against it.\nBring as many pages from this tome as you can find.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nWhat have you been able to find?\nCompletion.\nExcellent work. This tome should prove quite enlightening.\nNotes.\nThe quest item is looted upon a successful completion of a &lt;a href=\"Vision%20of%20N%27Zoth\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "658525", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=658525", "title": "Reconstructing \"The Curse of Stone\" (2)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"The Curse of Stone\" from Horrific Visions for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;\nDescription.\nThus far, the contents of this book are unsettling to say the least. Nevertheless, I have been able to glean valuable information on the nature of &lt;a href=\"N%27Zoth\"&gt;N'Zoth&lt;/a&gt;'s power, and have made alterations to &lt;a href=\"Ashjra%27kamas%2C%20Shroud%20of%20Resolve\"&gt;your cloak&lt;/a&gt; accordingly.\nThere remains much to learn, however. Continue your search for additional pages as you delve into the visions. \nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nUrgent matters require a great deal of attention. Unless it is of the utmost importance, I must see to my work. \nCompletion.\nFine work, indeed.\nNotes.\nThe quest item is looted upon a successful completion of a &lt;a href=\"Vision%20of%20N%27Zoth\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "658526", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=658526", "title": "Reconstructing \"The Curse of Stone\" (3)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"The Curse of Stone\" from Horrific Visions for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;\nDescription.\n&lt;a href=\"N%27Zoth\"&gt;N'Zoth&lt;/a&gt; is nothing if not subtle and insidious. I can see how an impressionable mind could be turned against the &lt;a href=\"Titan\"&gt;Titan&lt;/a&gt;s by reading these words. Thankfully, we are not so susceptible to such manipulation, are we?\nThe book is nearly complete. Continue retrieving its pages from within the visions. \nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nI believe we are on the precipice of a something grand.\nCompletion.\nA job well done, &lt;name&gt;.\nIt's time we advanced our efforts. \nNotes.\nThe quest item is looted upon a successful completion of a &lt;a href=\"Vision%20of%20N%27Zoth\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt;."}
{"id": "658563", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=658563", "title": "Reconstructing \"The Final Truth\"", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"The Final Truth\" from Lost Areas within &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Vision\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt;s for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nI know of this book. It is a sacred tome to those who worship the &lt;a href=\"Old%20God\"&gt;Old God&lt;/a&gt;s, containing the deepest secrets and most incomprehensible mysteries of the &lt;a href=\"Void\"&gt;Void&lt;/a&gt;. Only the most devout &lt;a href=\"cultist\"&gt;cultist&lt;/a&gt;s are allowed to gaze upon its pages.\nEven incomplete, holding it makes my skin crawl. I must take care not to read too much of it in a single sitting.\nThat being said, we must find its missing pages in order to continue our research. Retrieve them from the darkest corners of &lt;a href=\"N%27Zoth\"&gt;N'Zoth&lt;/a&gt;'s visions.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nI often find my own thoughts wandering, weary of what lies ahead.\nHow are you faring, &lt;name&gt;? Have you any news.\nCompletion.\nAnother piece falls into place. We are so very close, &lt;name&gt;.\nNotes.\nBefore \"Shadowlands\", 4 quest items were the objective."}
{"id": "658564", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=658564", "title": "Reconstructing \"The Final Truth\" (2)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"The Final Truth\" from Lost Areas within &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Vision\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt;s for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nI dare not repeat aloud the horrors that are recorded in these pages. The words themselves seem to shift and morph as I read them, as if the book itself is attempting to induce a descent into madness.\nThis is taxing work, but it is necessary if we are to fully prepare you for the dangers of &lt;a href=\"Ny%27alotha\"&gt;Ny'alotha&lt;/a&gt;. For as disturbing as its descriptions might be, setting foot within it will prove more challenging by an order of magnitude.\nKeep looking for pages from the book, &lt;name&gt;. But... leave the reading to me.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nYour success has brought us this far, &lt;name&gt;. Perhaps you have something to share?\nCompletion.\nOur journey's end approaches. The darkness gathers.\nNotes.\nBefore \"Shadowlands\", 6 quest items were the objective."}
{"id": "663191", "revid": "22514", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=663191", "title": "Reconstructing \"The Final Truth\" (3)", "text": "Objectives.\nCollect Torn Pages of \"The Final Truth\" from Lost Areas within &lt;a href=\"Horrific%20Vision\"&gt;Horrific Vision&lt;/a&gt;s for &lt;a href=\"Wrathion\"&gt;Wrathion&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Chamber%20of%20Heart\"&gt;Chamber of Heart&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nLong have I studied the secrets of the &lt;a href=\"Old%20God\"&gt;Old God&lt;/a&gt;s. I have traversed the whole of &lt;a href=\"Azeroth\"&gt;Azeroth&lt;/a&gt; in search of esoteric texts, lost archives, and forbidden knowledge, all in the name of preparing for the horror to come.\nNo amount of research could have prepared me for the depths of insanity I would find within this book. A madness so absolute that only the &lt;a href=\"Shath%27Yar\"&gt;Shath'Yar&lt;/a&gt; language can convey it.\nFind me the final pages of this accursed tome, &lt;name&gt;. I wish to learn what I need from it and be done with it forever.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nThe whispers of &lt;a href=\"Ny%27alotha\"&gt;Ny'alotha&lt;/a&gt; surround us. I believe you are ready for the final task, are you not?\nCompletion.\nThe works are complete. Together, they tell the tale of a descent into complete madness. How one deception leads to another, until reality itself is held in contempt. There is no \"truth\" to be found here.\nNo longer should you feel the need to run from the whispers, &lt;name&gt;. You are ready to silence them.\nNotes.\nBefore \"Shadowlands\", 8 quest items were the objective."}
