{"id": "33098", "revid": "40890366", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=33098", "title": "Bloodsail Hold", "text": "Bloodsail Hold is the home of the &lt;a href=\"Bloodsail%20Buccaneers\"&gt;Bloodsail Buccaneers&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Plunder%20Isle\"&gt;Plunder Isle&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn the RPG.\nBloodsail Hold is a large fortress that stands atop &lt;a href=\"Plunder%20Isle\"&gt;Plunder Isle&lt;/a&gt;'s west coast, and is well protected and strategically located. It was built by &lt;a href=\"Duke%20Falrevere\"&gt;Duke Falrevere&lt;/a&gt;, a former &lt;a href=\"Lordaeron%20%28kingdom%29\"&gt;Lordaeronian&lt;/a&gt; noble. He holds court here when he is not leading his &lt;a href=\"Bloodsail%20Buccaneers\"&gt;Bloodsail Buccaneers&lt;/a&gt; to battle against merchant ships or the &lt;a href=\"Blackwater%20Raiders\"&gt;Blackwater Raiders&lt;/a&gt;. Because &lt;a href=\"murloc\"&gt;murloc&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"basilisk\"&gt;basilisk&lt;/a&gt;s inhabit the island's eastern portion, the pirates don't really worry about an attack from that direction, but they take suitable precautions against naval attacks from the west. Numerous &lt;a href=\"cannon\"&gt;cannon&lt;/a&gt;s bristle from Bloodsail Hold, pointing west into the ocean.\n&lt;a href=\"Wallace%20Boltscrew\"&gt;Wallace Boltscrew&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Annetta%20Crank\"&gt;Annetta Crank&lt;/a&gt; have crafted several &lt;a href=\"submarine\"&gt;submarine&lt;/a&gt;s that could prove extremely dangerous. Duke Falrevere is holding these vessels secretly beneath Bloodsail Hold for now, for fear of tipping his hand to the Blackwater Raiders before he is ready. Falrevere spends almost all his time aboard the \"&lt;a href=\"Devil%20Shark\"&gt;Devil Shark&lt;/a&gt;\" and stops off in Bloodsail Hold only occasionally."}
