{"id": "102609", "revid": "49848256", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=102609", "title": "Bloodscalp Clan Heads", "text": "In Bloodscalp Clan Heads, you must defeat the chief and witchdoctor of the &lt;a href=\"Bloodscalp\"&gt;Bloodscalp&lt;/a&gt;s and take their heads back to &lt;a href=\"Grom%27gol%20Base%20Camp\"&gt;Grom'gol&lt;/a&gt;. This quest is in a long chain, all available in Grom'gol, the first being &lt;a href=\"Hunt%20for%20Yenniku\"&gt;Hunt for Yenniku&lt;/a&gt; which can be obtained from &lt;a href=\"Nimboya\"&gt;Nimboya&lt;/a&gt;.\nObjectives.\nBring Gan'zulah's Head and Nezzliok's Head to the &lt;a href=\"Bubbling%20Cauldron\"&gt;bubbling cauldron&lt;/a&gt; at the Grom'gol Base Camp.\nDescription.\nYenniku was not among the heads, and I thank the Great Serpent for it. But we are no closer to finding him.\nWe must know the truth, and I fear that only the Bloodscalp chief and his witchdoctor know it. They are the enemies of the Darkspear tribe and will not speak freely, so we must force the truth from their dead lips!\nBring me the heads of Gan'zulah and Nezzliok the Dire and place them within this cauldron.\nThey are deep within Zul'Kunda. Bring their heads...we will then make them talk.\nRewards.\nYou will be rewarded with the following:\nProgress.\nThe greenish broth within the cauldron bubbles.\nCompletion.\nYou place the heads of Gan'zulah and Nezzliok within the cauldron...\nNotes.\nThese two trolls can be found in the ruins in north-western &lt;a href=\"Stranglethorn%20Vale\"&gt;Stranglethorn Vale&lt;/a&gt;, close to the beach. It is probably easiest to get to them from the beach side - just head as far north on the beach as you can and head up the ramps. The coordinates for &lt;a href=\"Gan%27zulah\"&gt;Gan'zulah&lt;/a&gt; are . &lt;a href=\"Nezzliok\"&gt;Nezzliok&lt;/a&gt; should be in the same area. If you can't find them at first just wait for a while, these two have very long respawn timers.\nTurn in the quest at the Bubbling Cauldron next to Nimboya at the north entrance to Grom'gol Base Camp. After you turn it in, click on the cauldron again to receive the next two quests in the chain."}
