k, &lt;a href=\"Leaving%20an%20Opening\"&gt;Leaving an Opening&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis completes the \"Remember to Close the Door\" criterion of &lt;a href=\"Eternally%20in%20the%20Vale\"&gt;Eternally in the Vale&lt;/a&gt;."}
