 priests are stuck under big pieces of metal. You can kick the wreckage away to free them, which will make them stand up, heal themselves and join the efforts on Shen-zin Su. Other healers are also being attacked by saurok, and they will help when freed from their attackers. Once OK, they will say one of these things:\nOn finishing the progress bar:\nOn complete, another cutscene. The flowing blood has stopped and trees are in the area. However, the Alliance\u2014Horde tensions look like they're flaring up... Speak to Ji to continue."}
