Silverback Gorilla&lt;/a&gt;. After killing this one, &lt;a href=\"Konda\"&gt;Konda&lt;/a&gt; will come running into the cave. Having disposed of \"Konda\", the player will finally face &lt;a href=\"Mokk%20the%20Savage\"&gt;Mokk the Savage&lt;/a&gt;.\nOnce dead, \"Mokk\" can be looted for the \"Heart of Mokk\", which can then be turned in to \"Fin Fizracket\" in &lt;a href=\"Booty%20Bay\"&gt;Booty Bay&lt;/a&gt;."}
