{"id": "438731", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=438731", "title": "Marauders of Darrowshire (Classic)", "text": "Marauders of Darrowshire is part of the &lt;a href=\"Rewriting%20the%20Battle%20of%20Darrowshire%20quest%20chain%20%28Classic%29\"&gt;Rewriting the Battle of Darrowshire quest chain (Classic)&lt;/a&gt;.\nObjectives.\nBring 5 Resonating Skulls and the Mystic Crystal to &lt;a href=\"Carlin%20Redpath\"&gt;Carlin Redpath&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Eastern%20Plaguelands\"&gt;Eastern Plaguelands&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\n&lt;a href=\"Chromie\"&gt;Chromie&lt;/a&gt; said the relics you gathered are reagents to a powerful spell, and one more is required: skulls from the scourge who took part in the &lt;a href=\"battle%20of%20Darrowshire\"&gt;battle of Darrowshire&lt;/a&gt;.\nTake this crystal and hunt &lt;a href=\"Scourge%20Champion\"&gt;scourge champions&lt;/a&gt; for their skulls. The crystal is enchanted; if a champion took part in the battle, then when you pass the crystal over its skull it will resonate. Bring me those resonating skulls.\nGo, &lt;name&gt;. You'll find scourge champions in the &lt;a href=\"Noxious%20Glade\"&gt;Noxious Glade&lt;/a&gt; to the north and the &lt;a href=\"Fungal%20Vale\"&gt;Fungal Vale&lt;/a&gt; to the west.\nRewards.\nYou will receive\nProgress.\nDo you have the skulls? Chromie said they will be critical for her spell, and that spell will give us the chance to save &lt;a href=\"Darrowshire\"&gt;Darrowshire&lt;/a&gt;.\nCompletion.\nYou found them! Wonderful!\nAlthough I don't fully understand how they can help us, I feel their power and I know in my bones that they are linked to my home village of Darrowshire."}
