{"id": "283112", "revid": "42038977", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=283112", "title": "Marcus (gladiator)", "text": "Marcus is a human &lt;a href=\"fighter\"&gt;fighter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"gladiator\"&gt;gladiator&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Gurubashi%20Arena\"&gt;Arena&lt;/a&gt; of &lt;a href=\"Stranglethorn%20Vale\"&gt;Stranglethorn Vale&lt;/a&gt;. He is a male human of about 45 years. He was once encountered by a group of escaping adventurers. It occurred during a battle outside, the shockwave were damaging portions of the structure causing plaster from of the roof to drop. Marcus wasn't looking for a fight, and told them to get the hell out before the trolls came back. He noticed that a few of the escapees were carrying extra weapons, and asked for one, and let them know their were children trapped further down the hall. Marcus helped free children, and ran towards the stairs to escape before the ceiling collapsed."}
{"id": "151143", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=151143", "title": "Marcus (paladin)", "text": "Marcus is a well-traveled &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"paladin\"&gt;paladin&lt;/a&gt; and the main character of the erotic \"&lt;a href=\"Steamy%20Romance%20Novel\"&gt;Steamy Romance Novel&lt;/a&gt;s\" series. He owns a &lt;a href=\"warhorse\"&gt;warhorse&lt;/a&gt;.\nBiography.\nAs detailed in several romance novels, Marcus had flings with the &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"mage\"&gt;mage&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Nahni\"&gt;Nahni&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Forsaken\"&gt;Forsaken&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"rogue\"&gt;rogue&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Ah%27tusa\"&gt;Ah'tusa&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"gnome\"&gt;gnome&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"warlock\"&gt;warlock&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Tavi\"&gt;Tavi&lt;/a&gt;, and the &lt;a href=\"draenei\"&gt;draenei&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Soola\"&gt;Soola&lt;/a&gt;. He also went on a blind date with the &lt;a href=\"goblin\"&gt;goblin&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Revi%20Ramrod\"&gt;Revi Ramrod&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Pandaria\"&gt;Pandaria&lt;/a&gt;, he visited the &lt;a href=\"Tavern%20in%20the%20Mists\"&gt;Tavern in the Mists&lt;/a&gt;, where he met &lt;a href=\"Kama%20the%20Beast%20Tamer\"&gt;Kama the Beast Tamer&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Madam%20Goya\"&gt;Madam Goya&lt;/a&gt;, and flirted with two unnamed &lt;a href=\"blood%20elf\"&gt;blood elves&lt;/a&gt;. He later traveled to , where he visited &lt;a href=\"Lunarfall\"&gt;Lunarfall&lt;/a&gt; and had an encounter with the stable master &lt;a href=\"Raven%20%28human%20male%29\"&gt;Raven&lt;/a&gt;.\nLegion.\nMarcus makes his first in-game appearance in a hut just east of the upper level of &lt;a href=\"Thunder%20Totem\"&gt;Thunder Totem&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Highmountain\"&gt;Highmountain&lt;/a&gt;, where he can be seen waking up beside the &lt;a href=\"tauren\"&gt;tauren&lt;/a&gt; couple &lt;a href=\"Tanda%20Freeseeker\"&gt;Tanda&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Bax%20Freeseeker\"&gt;Bax Freeseeker&lt;/a&gt;, before walking out of the hut and disappearing with the following words:\nThe encounter is the subject of . A \"Steamy Jewelry Box\" inside the hut contains a &lt;a href=\"Shiny%20Silver%20Necklace\"&gt;Shiny Silver Necklace&lt;/a&gt;.\nLater in his travels, Marcus meets a &lt;a href=\"Kul%20Tiras\"&gt;Kul Tiran&lt;/a&gt; pirate woman and a &lt;a href=\"dracthyr\"&gt;dracthyr&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"mage\"&gt;mage&lt;/a&gt;, though it should be noted that dracthyr in-game can only be &lt;a href=\"evoker\"&gt;evoker&lt;/a&gt;s.\nBooks.\nHe is the main character of:\nHe is mentioned in:\nVideos.\n&lt;vplayer/&gt;"}
