{"id": "509717", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=509717", "title": "Maribeth", "text": "Maribeth is a &lt;a href=\"nightborne\"&gt;nightborne&lt;/a&gt; initially located at &lt;a href=\"The%20Waning%20Crescent\"&gt;The Waning Crescent&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Suramar\"&gt;Suramar&lt;/a&gt;. She worked as an &lt;a href=\"innkeeper\"&gt;innkeeper&lt;/a&gt; inside one of the tavern's buildings, presumably employed by the owner, &lt;a href=\"Vanthir\"&gt;Vanthir&lt;/a&gt;.\nDuring the &lt;a href=\"Suramar%20storyline%23Insurrection\"&gt;Insurrection&lt;/a&gt;, Maribeth and several other nightborne were captured during the massacre of the Waning Crescent and taken to a landing area above &lt;a href=\"Felsoul%20Hold\"&gt;Felsoul Hold&lt;/a&gt;. After the adventurer rescues Maribeth and the other prisoners, they take a boat ride to the &lt;a href=\"Evermoon%20Terrace\"&gt;Evermoon Terrace&lt;/a&gt; in the city and with &lt;a href=\"Silgryn\"&gt;Silgryn&lt;/a&gt;'s help, relocates to the safety of Shal'Aran. Following &lt;a href=\"Elisande\"&gt;Elisande&lt;/a&gt;'s demise, she and the other Nightfallen relocated to the &lt;a href=\"Nighthold\"&gt;Nighthold&lt;/a&gt;.\nShe joined the &lt;a href=\"Dragonscale%20Expedition\"&gt;Dragonscale Expedition&lt;/a&gt; and traveled to the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Isles\"&gt;Dragon Isles&lt;/a&gt;. She can be found at the &lt;a href=\"Dragonscale%20Basecamp\"&gt;Dragonscale Basecamp&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Waking%20Shores\"&gt;Waking Shores&lt;/a&gt;.\nQuotes.\n&lt;br&gt;\nYou may rest from your travels and your studies here, friend.\nA hot meal and a cool dip in the water are the biggest adventures I seek nowadays.\n&lt;br&gt;"}
